<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="kr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>유저 정보 수정</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-rbsA2VBKQhggwzxH7pPCaAqO46MgnOM80zW1RWuH61DGLwZJEdK2Kadq2F9CUG65" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/reset.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/memberUpdate.css">
</head>
<body>
<div id="wrap">
    <header id="header">
        <div class="logo-box">
            <a href="/main">
                <div class="logo">Handy</div>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="user-profile">
            <!-- 프로필 이미지 -->
            <div class="profile-img">
                <img src="/img/ico-chatting.png" alt="프로필 테스트 이미지">
            </div>
            <div class="profile-right">
                <button id="img-edit-btn">+</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="user-tool">
            <a href="/logout">로그아웃</a>
        </div>
    </header>
    <main class="container">
        <div class="form-box">
            <p>회원 정보 수정</p>
            <form action="/mypage/member/update" method="post">
                <input type="hidden" name="_method" value="put">
                <input type="hidden" name="id" value="{{currentMember.id}}">
                <div class="userId-area area">
                    <label for="userId">아이디</label>
                    <input type="text" name="userId" id="userId" value="{{currentMember.userId}}" readonly>
                </div>
                <div class="nickName-area area">
                    <label for="nickName">닉네임</label>
                    <input type="text" name="nickName" id="nickName" value="{{currentMember.nickName}}">
                </div>
                <div class="password-area area">
                    <label for="passWord">비밀번호</label>
                    <input type="password" name="password" id="password">
                </div>
                <div class="password-check-area area">
                    <label for="passWord">비밀번호 확인</label>
                    <input type="password" name="check-password" id="check-password">
                </div>
                <div class="email-area area">
                    <label for="email">이메일</label>
                    <input type="email" name="email" id="email" value="{{currentMember.email}}" readonly>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" id="update-btn" onclick="return returnSubmit()">수정하기</button>
                {{#errorMessage}}
                <span>{{errorMessage}}</span>
                {{/errorMessage}}
            </form>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer id="footer">
        <div>
            <p>본 사이트는 상업적 목적이 아닌 개인 포트폴리오 용도로 제작되었습니다. </p>
            <p>홈페이지 일부 내용과 기타 이미지 등은 출처가 따로 있음을 밝힙니다.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</div>

</body>
<script src="/js/memberUpdate.js"></script>
</html>